nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM PK model 1 cmt base
$INPUT ID TIME MDV EVID DV AMT SEX WT ETN $DATA ../../../../../acop.csv IGNORE=@ $SUBROUTINES ADVAN2 TRANS2
$PK ET=1 IF(ETN.EQ.3) ET=1.3 KA = THETA(1)*EXP(ETA(1)) CL = THETA(2)*((WT/70)**0.75)* EXP(ETA(2)) V = THETA(3)*EXP(ETA(3)) SC=V
$THETA (0, 2) ; KA (0, 3) ; CL (0, 10) ; V2 (0.02) ; RUVp (1) ; RUVa
$OMEGA 0.04 $OMEGA BLOCK(2) 0.05 ; iiv CL 0.01 0.2 ; iiv V2
$SIGMA 1 FIX
$ERROR IPRED = F IRES = DV-IPRED W = IPRED*THETA(4) + THETA(5) IF (W.EQ.0) W = 1 IWRES = IRES/W Y= IPRED+W*ERR(1)
$EST METHOD=1 INTERACTION MAXEVAL=9999 SIG=3 PRINT=5 NOABORT POSTHOC $COV
